Description/Plot 
in English

Just before we say goodbye to 2011, Sirina Entertainment makes the excess. This time the protagonists meeting place in women's prison! It is no exaggeration to say that the new production of Sirina covers all sexual tastes and ... vices! The imagination is beyond any expectation, since the script wants to seduce policewomen prisoners, prisoners are erotic tool in the hands of corrupt police and young girls engaging in wild sex in their cells, sometimes alone and sometimes have to suffer the violent behavior of their jailers.

In the movie "Scandal in women's prisons" Christina Katerina and Rousaki Tsopei meet the emerging Elena Kallianos and 19 year old Dina, the new star of Sirina and this makes its maiden debut!
